      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/4/5/4",
      "text": [
        ": قلت لابي الحسن الرضا عليه السلام: روينا أن الله علم لاجهل فيه، حياة لاموت فيه، نور لاظلمة فيه قال: كذلك هو"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "4. [4/341] al-Tawhid: Ibn al-Walid from al-Saffar from al-Yaqtini from Yunus who said: I said to Abi al-Hasan al-Ridha عليه السلام: We have narrated that Allah is Knowledge with no ignorance in Him. Life with no death in Him. Light with no darkness in Him. He said: That is who He is."
        ]
      }
    },
